Provident Online






Our Provident Online service is designed and offered to customers of Provident Trust Company to access their account information 24 hours a day, seven days a week.  By utilizing Provident Online customers of Provident Trust Company can:

Easily change their view of account holdings and view all assets or a specific asset type.
Easily view acquisition dates and cost basis information for all holdings.
View account transactions in a summary or detail format.
View pending trades.
Utilize the cash forecasting tool for receipts and disbursements.
Download transactions to Microsoft Money.
Download asset or transaction information to an Excel spreadsheet.
Create custom downloads of account holdings or transactions.
Link to various financial websites.
View and receive statements in electronic format.
