As the Baby Boomer population continues to grow, the price of retirement homes in desirable locations from Arizona to the South of Spain continues to rise. Using self-directed IRAs, some investors are now purchasing these retirement dream homes well before their retirement years. Foreseeing a rise in the cost of retirement properties, most notably waterfront properties…
