About






Provident Trust Company is the largest independent fiduciary in the state of Nebraska. For nearly 20 years, we have helped hundreds of families, businesses, organizations and institutions meet their wealth management goals. Today our team consists of experienced professionals who have the solutions to help you and your family establish, grow, manage and safeguard your wealth.
Provident Trust Company holds itself to the highest of fiduciary standards. As a result, we maintain a strong focus on meeting the needs of our trust customers and exceeding their expectations. In fact, we deliver more than just positive investment returns and competent administration; we provide our customers with the personal service they expect and deserve.
By working with a limited number of customers, our trust officers and portfolio managers are able to closely monitor the day-to-day management of each account, take the time to understand individual needs and objectives, and develop long-term, mutually beneficial relationships with our trust customers. We pride ourselves on offering our customers a comprehensive financial management strategy that integrates the customer’s financial goals with their time horizon, tax situation, risk tolerance and specific circumstances; all while providing effective wealth management solutions with no hidden fees.
Perhaps the most important service we offer our customers, however, is the competent administration of their trusts and estates. This means more than just a simple transfer of assets. By leaving property in trust and naming Provident Trust Company as trustee, our customers ensure that the process will be managed by a team of experienced professionals who they can rely on to provide their loved ones with thoughtful and exceptional personal service. 
 



