Review of: Provident Trust GroupReviewed by: Tom SmallwoodRating:3On December 8, 2015Last modified:December 27, 2016Summary:Provident Trust Group is an independent corporate trust company located in Las Vegas, Nevada. By relying on Provident as your fiduciary, we can provide you with access to the many advantages afforded by trusts under Nevada law regardless of where you live.About Provident Trust Group
Provident Trust Group is a an independent and licensed corporate trust company that administers custodial services and focuses on self-directed IRAs, fund administration, and investment opportunities for retirees.
The company first started in 2003 by assisting individuals turn their self-directed IRAs into fund sources which can be used to start new businesses.
It briefly stopped its operations in 2009 to give way to an investigation conducted by the IRS to prove that its business model did not violate any regulations by the organization.
